(42, 7, 42, 23, 44, 22, 22, NULL, 'Forgiveness and Redemption', 'This connection highlights the theme of forgiveness in both passages. Luke 7:42 speaks of forgiveness and love, while Isaiah 44:22 emphasizes the act of blotted out transgressions and redemption.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 7, 42, 24, 31, 33, 34, NULL, 'Forgiveness and Love Connection', 'This connection highlights the theme of forgiveness in both passages. In Luke, the act of forgiving leads to love, while in Jeremiah, God promises to forgive iniquity, fostering a deep relationship with His people.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
